-- China Says `Appropriate Environment' Is Needed for Gas Talks, Kyodo Says
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   R e y n o l d s
-- 2010-11-14T03:20:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-14/china-says-appropriate-environment-is-needed-for-gas-talks-kyodo-says.html
China’s Foreign Minister Yang Jiechi
said “an appropriate environment is necessary for the
resumption” of talks with Japan over the development of gas
fields in the East China Sea, Kyodo News reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
